    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13211#issuecomment-4329973065\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13211\">issue #13211</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for filing this issue!</p>\n<p>I'm actually somewhat perplexed looking at our internal discussions from this CVE: we agreed to patch v36, v40, v41, but somehow it never came up (and I will take primary responsibility for not realizing!) that we should have patched v24 as well, since it is still in LTS.</p>\n<p>I'll do a backport and then do a version-bump release; thanks.</p>\n</blockquote>",
